data.description:
Welcome to Thunderbird Palms Living! This 2BD, 2BA patio home offers freedom with no HOA. The screened-in patio and inviting yard set the scene for relaxed living. Inside, enjoy low utility bills with Tesla solar power, plus recent upgrades like new carpet, fresh paint, can lights, water softener, reverse osmosis system, and water heater.  Both BA's have also been recently updated.

The 1-car garage with built-in cabinets adds practicality. Step outside to a tiled patio, perfect for gatherings or potential RV parking. Ideally located near Banner Thunderbird Hospital, shopping, dining, Glendale College, ASU West, Midwestern University, & major freeways. Explore the nearby sports facility park for an active lifestyle. Welcome to Thunderbird Palms Living!
